    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic vehicle! It's in great shape and has been well-maintained, offering a reliable and smooth driving experience. While it shows a bit of character from regular use, it remains a solid, high-quality choice for anyone looking for a dependable and attractive ride.",
